        Buyer's Agent Commission in Brisbane: What Sellers Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Buyer's agents are more active in Brisbane's inner east than ever. Understanding how they are paid, how conjunctional arrangements work, and what their involvement means for your negotiation will help you handle buyer's agent-represented offers with confidence.
      </p>
